---
// Seção explicando para quem é o app - SEO focado em todos os perfis
---

<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white dark:from-black dark:to-gray-900 py-16">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white sm:text-4xl mb-4">
        Para Todas as Mulheres que Viajam
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        Seja qual for seu estilo de viagem, o Viajadoras é para você
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Viajando Sozinha -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-100 dark:bg-brand-900/30 text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
