        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
          Socialização em Viagens
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          Faça novos contatos, participe de eventos e encontros, compartilhe experiências e crie conexões reais com mulheres viajantes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Rede de Apoio -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-emerald-100 dark:bg-emerald-900/30 text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
          Apenas Rede de Apoio
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          Não busca companhia, mas quer segurança? Use check-ins, contatos de confiança e tenha acesso ao suporte da comunidade quando precisar.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Mochileiras e Aventureiras -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">
